We'll stop all treatment, no dialysis.

1688
01:52:35,009 --> 01:52:37,535
Even stop feeding if you like.

1689
01:52:37,712 --> 01:52:41,513
You'll be in a coma in a few days.
Dead in a week, two at most.

1690
01:52:41,818 --> 01:52:44,515
